{"id":721633,"date":[{"year":1986,"month":4,"day":8}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"121","ytitle":"","mtitle":"悼江泽宏教授","ftitle":"","authors":["汪尧田"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪尧田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复旦大学世界经济研究所所长江泽宏教授病逝。余与泽宏四十余年来谊同管鲍，闻噩耗，思以诗悼之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年前几少年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同窗剪烛议兴亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宏论总能惊四座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿心忧国见文章；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执教江湾旦复旦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芬芳桃李满江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那堪九十一天病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春申处处哭江郎。"}]}